## Summary Table: Pros and Cons of Gun Ownership

| **Pros**                                         | **Cons**                                         |
|-------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------|
| Self-defense and protection against crime        | Risk of accidental shootings and injuries       |
| Constitutional right and symbol of freedom       | Increased risk of suicide and domestic homicide |
| Hunting and food procurement                      | Psychological fear and intimidation             |
| Financial asset and potential appreciation        | High financial costs (purchase, ammo, training) |
| Skill development and recreational enjoyment     | Inadequate training leading to misuse            |
| Deterrence effect in confrontations               | Potential increase in overall gun violence       |

